{"id":"ceeb61fd5c06efca4ddc71f3c3cbfa95bd7d1721","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1228353","title":"我开发了一个开源版 Surge，把 Mac 变成可导入规则、可按设备分流的全屋透明代理网关。","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"wsy95613373","excerpt":"分享创造 - @wsy95613373 - OpenSurge for Mac 是一个开源应用，提供类似 Surge 的体验，可以把你的 Mac 变成全屋的代理网关：同一局域网里的手机、电视、PS5 、游戏机、VR 设备和虚拟机，无需逐台设置代","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div><p>OpenSurge for Mac 是一个开源应用，提供类似 Surge 的体验，可以把你的 Mac 变成全屋的代理网关：同一局域网里的手机、电视、PS5 、游戏机、VR 设备和虚拟机，无需逐台设置代理；设备一接入网络，便自动通过 Mac 的全屋代理网关，并按各自策略选择直连或代理出口。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WS4dl0V.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WS4dl0V.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a></p><p>你可以为每台设备设置不同的出口策略：手机和 Mac 一起走代理、游戏机连美服、电视走流媒体节点。DHCP/DNS 、分流策略和流量状态，都由 OpenSurge 集中管理。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0hwnbG7.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0hwnbG7.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a></p><p>- 可导入已有的 mihomo 配置或订阅，保留原有节点、代理组和规则<br>- Web GUI 实时展示每台设备的连接、上下行流量和实际出口链；菜单栏随时查看网关状态与恢复提醒。<br>- 底层由 dnsmasq 提供 DHCP/DNS ，mihomo 负责代理与策略，macOS pf 和 IPv4 forwarding 提供 NAT 与转发。</p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://i.imgur.com/ubAeY1G.png\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ubAeY1G.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"></a></p><p>仓库链接在下面：<br>🔗 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/YTwsy/OpenSurge-for-Mac\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://github.com/YTwsy/OpenSurge-for-Mac</a></p></div><div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/Surge\"><li></li> Surge</a><a href=\"/tag/网关\"><li></li> 网关</a><a href=\"/tag/分流\"><li></li> 分流</a></P><p><span>35 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-20 12:00:47 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17880739\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64d6/6ac2/51170_normal.png?m=1784387864\" alt=\"Tink\" data-uid=\"51170\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Tink\">Tink</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 16:17:56 +08:00\">22h 53m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>牛的老哥</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17880874\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3da6/bca1/579014_normal.png?m=1655454180\" alt=\"xubeiyou\" data-uid=\"579014\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/xubeiyou\">xubeiyou</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 17:33:54 +08:00\">21h 37m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>说实话前段时间我也有想法写一个 但是后面事情太多了就没去处理 还是用的 verge 。兄弟牛！希望越做好越好 ！</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17880990\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/97f7855545ae7078b5500d6694e3c8f1?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"leena\" data-uid=\"373521\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>7</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/leena\">leena</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 19:03:44 +08:00\">20h 7m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>会有 Windows 版和安卓版么</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17880995\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f52b/3b73/609073_normal.png?m=1783843767\" alt=\"jackenliu\" data-uid=\"609073\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>8</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/jackenliu\">jackenliu</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 19:10:24 +08:00\">20h 0m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>牛啊，有 surge 那么稳定吗？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881066\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/66b3/f079/792507_normal.png?m=1781351440\" alt=\"nc\" data-uid=\"792507\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>9</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/nc\">nc</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 20:08:53 +08:00\">19h 2m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 3</span>\n                    \n                    <p>Surge 它又不是 Adobe 这种商业软件，独立开发者的软件，你用 AI clone 一个不完全版名字前面加个 Open ，这样不好。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881068\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e92c/81b3/163500_normal.png?m=1531980501\" alt=\"skusdk\" data-uid=\"163500\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>11</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/skusdk\">skusdk</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 20:10:19 +08:00\">19h 0m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>对比 surge 比它好用吗</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881102\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ed5/5204/621478_normal.png?m=1784445264\" alt=\"wsy95613373\" data-uid=\"621478\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>12</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wsy95613373\">wsy95613373</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 20:30:35 +08:00\">18h 40m ago via Android</span> \n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/skusdk\">skusdk</a> 支持的，OpenSurge 不自己解析协议，而是把 proxies 透传给 mihomo 内核。换句话说就是只要 mihomo 内核能支持，OpenSurge 就支持[害羞 R]</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881273\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5a60/ef6c/110971_normal.png?m=1765452305\" alt=\"goodryb\" data-uid=\"110971\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>16</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/goodryb\">goodryb</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 22:21:08 +08:00\">16h 50m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>可以啊，假以时日必成大器</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881284\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a4ee/59dd/7751_normal.png?m=1751373218\" alt=\"Visoar\" data-uid=\"7751\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>17</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Visoar\">Visoar</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 22:31:19 +08:00\">16h 39m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>还以为是写了个新内核，但看起来是 mihomo skin ...？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881314\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a690beda8e548d5eabf9a5c2ef6d010e?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"lw0717\" data-uid=\"273766\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>18</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/lw0717\">lw0717</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 22:54:46 +08:00\">16h 16m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>兄弟 6p 已点星</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881374\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ed5/5204/621478_normal.png?m=1784445264\" alt=\"wsy95613373\" data-uid=\"621478\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>19</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wsy95613373\">wsy95613373</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 23:29:48 +08:00\">15h 41m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/Visoar\">Visoar</a> 一部分功能有关 DHCP/DNS 的分发，这样可以让局域网下的其他设备无感接入，并分别为其他设备设定分流规则和不同的出口，类似 Surge 的网关模式——自动 DHCP 。这部分之前没有见到有 mihomo skin 去做，想实现类似功能只能用软路由+OpenClash 或者类似的路由器方案</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881387\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64d6/6ac2/51170_normal.png?m=1784387864\" alt=\"Tink\" data-uid=\"51170\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>20</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Tink\">Tink</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 23:40:13 +08:00\">15h 30m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>退出不了。</p><p>另外想当旁路由用，应该选第一个模式还是第二个？</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881409\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ed5/5204/621478_normal.png?m=1784445264\" alt=\"wsy95613373\" data-uid=\"621478\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>21</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wsy95613373\">wsy95613373</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 00:00:13 +08:00\">15h 10m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/Tink\">Tink</a> 不好意思，我已经定位到问题了，swiftUI 的回调有点小问题，新的 Release 已经修复了。应该是第二个，主路由继续提供 DHCP ，只把需要代理的设备网关和 DNS 指向 Mac 。第三个模式的话看你要不要再接个 AP 路由器了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881420\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64d6/6ac2/51170_normal.png?m=1784387864\" alt=\"Tink\" data-uid=\"51170\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>23</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Tink\">Tink</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 00:06:42 +08:00\">15h 4m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/wsy95613373\">wsy95613373</a> 配置成第二个之后，下方的“MAC 网关 IPv4（192.168.50.1）”和 DHCP 池起始点 相当于都是无效的对吧？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881442\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7ed5/5204/621478_normal.png?m=1784445264\" alt=\"wsy95613373\" data-uid=\"621478\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>24</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wsy95613373\">wsy95613373</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 00:20:24 +08:00\">14h 50m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/Tink\">Tink</a> 第二个模式 MAC 网关 IPv4 有效且必填，客户端手工把网关和 DNS 指向它。但 DHCP 池确实是运行时无效的，更合理的表现应该是把整组 DHCP 字段置灰，我明天修改下。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881450\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/64d6/6ac2/51170_normal.png?m=1784387864\" alt=\"Tink\" data-uid=\"51170\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>25</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Tink\">Tink</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 00:30:39 +08:00\">14h 40m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>@<a href=\"/member/wsy95613373\">wsy95613373</a> 哦那我理解有误。</p><p>比如我 MacOS 当前有且仅有无线网络，IP 是 192.168.5.123，则这个“MAC 网关 IPv4”就填 192.168.5.123 即可？</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881488\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4b02/f68a/466273_normal.png?m=1579656258\" alt=\"chooy\" data-uid=\"466273\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>26</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/chooy\">chooy</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 01:04:02 +08:00\">14h 7m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>是否提供 brew install</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881532\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/326b525245435e15befb7f38bce37ba9?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"mooyo\" data-uid=\"401342\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>28</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/mooyo\">mooyo</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 02:05:54 +08:00\">13h 5m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>既然是 mihomo ，按理说应该能做 linux/openwrt 版？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882066\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a434a3b21fe7a3581b4c5f1f3102ae90?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"vzyw\" data-uid=\"132931\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>33</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/vzyw\">vzyw</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 09:59:17 +08:00\">5h 11m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>就差抓包功能了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882990\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2dfd/eb78/299970_normal.png?m=1666570950\" alt=\"teky\" data-uid=\"299970\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>34</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/teky\">teky</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 12:00:45 +08:00\">3h 10m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>牛哥，能否搞个 OpenSurge for Win ，感谢！</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17882991\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/dbc9/1eaf/89635_normal.png?m=1776671720\" alt=\"EthanZC\" data-uid=\"89635\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>35</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/EthanZC\">EthanZC</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 12:00:47 +08:00\">3h 10m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>大胆点,既然用的 mihomo, 就作为 clash 系来宣传</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n\n</div></DIV>","content_text":"OpenSurge for Mac 是一个开源应用，提供类似 Surge 的体验，可以把你的 Mac 变成全屋的代理网关：同一局域网里的手机、电视、PS5 、游戏机、VR 设备和虚拟机，无需逐台设置代理；设备一接入网络，便自动通过 Mac 的全屋代理网关，并按各自策略选择直连或代理出口。你可以为每台设备设置不同的出口策略：手机和 Mac 一起走代理、游戏机连美服、电视走流媒体节点。DHCP/DNS 、分流策略和流量状态，都由 OpenSurge 集中管理。- 可导入已有的 mihomo 配置或订阅，保留原有节点、代理组和规则- Web GUI 实时展示每台设备的连接、上下行流量和实际出口链；菜单栏随时查看网关状态与恢复提醒。- 底层由 dnsmasq 提供 DHCP/DNS ，mihomo 负责代理与策略，macOS pf 和 IPv4 forwarding 提供 NAT 与转发。仓库链接在下面：🔗 https://github.com/YTwsy/OpenSurge-for-Mac Surge 网关 分流35 replies • 2026-07-20 12:00:47 +08:00 1 Tink 22h 53m ago 牛的老哥 5 xubeiyou 21h 37m ago 说实话前段时间我也有想法写一个 但是后面事情太多了就没去处理 还是用的 verge 。兄弟牛！希望越做好越好 ！ 7 leena 20h 7m ago via iPhone 会有 Windows 版和安卓版么 8 jackenliu 20h 0m ago via iPhone 牛啊，有 surge 那么稳定吗？ 9 nc 19h 2m ago 3 Surge 它又不是 Adobe 这种商业软件，独立开发者的软件，你用 AI clone 一个不完全版名字前面加个 Open ，这样不好。 11 skusdk 19h 0m ago 对比 surge 比它好用吗 12 wsy95613373 OP 18h 40m ago via Android @skusdk 支持的，OpenSurge 不自己解析协议，而是把 proxies 透传给 mihomo 内核。换句话说就是只要 mihomo 内核能支持，OpenSurge 就支持[害羞 R] 16 goodryb 16h 50m ago 可以啊，假以时日必成大器 17 Visoar 16h 39m ago 还以为是写了个新内核，但看起来是 mihomo skin ...？ 18 lw0717 16h 16m ago 兄弟 6p 已点星 19 wsy95613373 OP 15h 41m ago @Visoar 一部分功能有关 DHCP/DNS 的分发，这样可以让局域网下的其他设备无感接入，并分别为其他设备设定分流规则和不同的出口，类似 Surge 的网关模式——自动 DHCP 。这部分之前没有见到有 mihomo skin 去做，想实现类似功能只能用软路由+OpenClash 或者类似的路由器方案 20 Tink 15h 30m ago 退出不了。另外想当旁路由用，应该选第一个模式还是第二个？ 21 wsy95613373 OP 15h 10m ago 1 @Tink 不好意思，我已经定位到问题了，swiftUI 的回调有点小问题，新的 Release 已经修复了。应该是第二个，主路由继续提供 DHCP ，只把需要代理的设备网关和 DNS 指向 Mac 。第三个模式的话看你要不要再接个 AP 路由器了 23 Tink 15h 4m ago @wsy95613373 配置成第二个之后，下方的“MAC 网关 IPv4（192.168.50.1）”和 DHCP 池起始点 相当于都是无效的对吧？ 24 wsy95613373 OP 14h 50m ago 1 @Tink 第二个模式 MAC 网关 IPv4 有效且必填，客户端手工把网关和 DNS 指向它。但 DHCP 池确实是运行时无效的，更合理的表现应该是把整组 DHCP 字段置灰，我明天修改下。 25 Tink 14h 40m ago @wsy95613373 哦那我理解有误。比如我 MacOS 当前有且仅有无线网络，IP 是 192.168.5.123，则这个“MAC 网关 IPv4”就填 192.168.5.123 即可？ 26 chooy 14h 7m ago 是否提供 brew install 28 mooyo 13h 5m ago 既然是 mihomo ，按理说应该能做 linux/openwrt 版？ 33 vzyw 5h 11m ago 就差抓包功能了 34 teky 3h 10m ago 牛哥，能否搞个 OpenSurge for Win ，感谢！ 35 EthanZC 3h 10m ago 大胆点,既然用的 mihomo, 就作为 clash 系来宣传","fetched_at":"2026-07-20T07:12:07.190Z","ok":true}